==Gameplay Notes==
===Special Mechanics===

* Able to equip seaplane bombers and fighters on Kai.
* Able to equip 8cm HA guns in Reinforcement expansions on Kai Ni/Kai Ni Toku
* Able to equip minisubs, tanks and landing craft on Kai Ni Toku

===Overview===

'''Kai:'''
* Decent firepower and torpedo.
* Low HP and armour.

'''Kai Ni:'''
* Decent firepower and torpedo

'''Kai Ni Toku:'''
* Excellent firepower and torpedo
* Decent defensive stats
* lower plane capacity

